--- Install Eclipse on your Windows System
--- Help-->Install New Software --> Enter https://aws.amazon.com/eclipse and select all listed Names and finish the install.

If there is error please find the missing bundle web address and paste in the

--- Help-->Install New Software --> URL and complete this install first and then again retry above steps for aws sdk install.


Connect to your AWS account and browse services:

AWS Tookit icon can be seen after installation. select preferences from drop down menu and enter:
Access Key ID and Secret Access Key, downloaded from "My Security Credentials" --> "Access Keys" --> Create New Access Key.
